.TH "nvme_init_set_features_resv_mask" 9 "nvme_init_set_features_resv_mask" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_set_features_resv_mask \- Initialize passthru command for Reservation Notification Mask
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_set_features_resv_mask
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u32 nsid "  ","
.BI "bool sv "  ","
.BI "__u32 mask "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "nsid" 12
Namespace ID
.IP "sv" 12
Save value across power states
.IP "mask" 12
Reservation Notification Mask Field
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Set Features command with
FID value NVME_FEAT_FID_RESV_MASK
